OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early rain in the east
OL,6,Fclearing, then dry for many with sunny
OL,7,Fperiods and feeling fairly pleasant
OL,8,Fwith light winds. Isolated showers may
OL,9,Fgraze western coasts before heavier
OL,10,Fshowers push eastwards during the
OL,11,Fevening. Freshening winds later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudier this evening with
OL,14,Fshowers pushing into the west. Turning
OL,15,Fwet and windy through the early hours
OL,16,Fwith outbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
