OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAn unsettled start with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,7,Fpersistent over the moors. Somewhat
OL,8,Fdrier into the afternoon through still
OL,9,Fdrizzle in places. Windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FFurther spells of rain on Monday with
OL,13,Flighter winds. Drier overall on
OL,14,FTuesday and Wednesday with higher
OL,15,Fpressure in charge. Staying mild with
OL,16,Fwinds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
